134
00:09:54.927 --> 00:09:57.930 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
それから ２年ほどして
士郎さんが生まれたんですよ

135
00:09:58.514 --> 00:10:01.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
でも 奥様は
お体が弱かったものですから―

136
00:10:01.642 --> 00:10:04.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
私が そばでずっと
お手伝いしてたんです

137
00:10:04.854 --> 00:10:07.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
士郎さんには 私のおっぱい
飲ませてあげたし―

138
00:10:07.690 --> 00:10:09.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
おしめも取っ替えてあげたし

139
00:10:09.483 --> 00:10:10.568 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
エヘヘヘ

140
00:10:14.780 --> 00:10:15.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
そんなわけで

141
00:10:15.865 --> 00:10:20.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
今も士郎さんのことが気がかりで
時々お顔を見に来るんですよ

142
00:10:21.037 --> 00:10:23.789 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
今日もね 何だか
胸騒ぎがするから

143
00:10:23.914 --> 00:10:25.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
士郎さんの所へ来てみたら

144
00:10:25.458 --> 00:10:29.420 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
まあ 風邪をこじらせて死にそうに
なってるじゃありませんか

145
00:10:29.545 --> 00:10:32.923 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
こんな生活
いつまでもしてたら治りませんよ

146
00:10:33.049 --> 00:10:35.676 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
早くお嫁さんを
もらってくだすったらねえ

147
00:10:36.177 --> 00:10:38.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（山岡）
うるさいな　飯まだ？

148
00:10:38.346 --> 00:10:39.764 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
じきですよ

149
00:10:39.889 --> 00:10:42.391 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
お腹すくと子どもみたいなの

150
00:10:42.850 --> 00:10:45.102 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
ところで
どっちが本命なんですか？

151
00:10:45.394 --> 00:10:46.270 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（２人）ええ？

152
00:10:47.188 --> 00:10:50.566 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あの 本命って 何のお話ですか？

153
00:10:50.858 --> 00:10:54.528 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
士郎さんの お嫁さん候補の本命は
どっちかってことですよ

154
00:10:55.154 --> 00:10:58.157 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
やめてくれよ おチヨさん
ゴホッ ゴホッ

155
00:10:58.282 --> 00:11:00.493 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
２人は ただの会社の
同僚なんだからさ

156
00:11:00.910 --> 00:11:03.913 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
誤解しないでくれよ
彼女たちにも悪いだろ

157
00:11:04.038 --> 00:11:05.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
何を言ってるんです？

158
00:11:05.873 --> 00:11:08.417 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
こんな きれいなお嬢さんが
２人して来てくれるなんて

159
00:11:08.542 --> 00:11:10.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
めったにないことですよ

160
00:11:10.503 --> 00:11:13.214 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
このチャンスを逃して
一体 どうするんです？

161
00:11:13.339 --> 00:11:15.174 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（山岡）
大きなお世話だよ

162
00:11:15.341 --> 00:11:16.717 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ゴホッ ゴホッ

163
00:11:16.842 --> 00:11:19.303 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
とにかく おかしなこと言うのは
よしてくれよ

164
00:11:19.428 --> 00:11:21.430 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
おちおち寝てられないからさ

165
00:11:23.099 --> 00:11:25.601 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
で 話は戻るけど 本命は？

166
00:11:25.810 --> 00:11:26.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
おチヨさん！

167
00:11:28.896 --> 00:11:29.730 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ハッ！

168
00:11:29.855 --> 00:11:30.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（二木）うん？
（おチヨ）え？

169
00:11:33.359 --> 00:11:34.735 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（男性）火事だー

170
00:11:43.411 --> 00:11:44.954 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（男性）火事だぞー

171
00:11:45.704 --> 00:11:46.580 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
大変だよ

172
00:11:54.338 --> 00:11:56.090 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（男性）火事だー

173
00:11:56.215 --> 00:11:57.758 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
火事だぞー！

174
00:11:58.759 --> 00:12:00.261 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（男性）119番だ

175
00:12:03.639 --> 00:12:06.183 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
火事だ 火事だ 火事だぞー！

176
00:12:06.308 --> 00:12:07.810 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
みんな来てくれー！

177
00:12:08.352 --> 00:12:09.728 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（おチヨ）まあ 大変

178
00:12:13.190 --> 00:12:13.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
え？

179
00:12:21.699 --> 00:12:22.533 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（２人）山岡さん

180
00:12:25.870 --> 00:12:27.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（二木）私(わたくし)も手伝うわ
（栗田）あ…

181
00:12:29.957 --> 00:12:31.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（おチヨ）待って！

182
00:12:32.168 --> 00:12:35.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
消火作業に お嬢さん方じゃ
役に立ちゃしません

183
00:12:37.256 --> 00:12:39.842 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
それより 消火作業のあと
手伝ってくれた人や

184
00:12:39.967 --> 00:12:41.177 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
火事にあったうちの人たちに

185
00:12:41.302 --> 00:12:43.888 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
何か体の温まる食べ物を
作ってあげたほうが

186
00:12:44.013 --> 00:12:45.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ずっと役に立ちます

187
00:12:46.765 --> 00:12:49.393 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
頑張って おいしいものを
作ってくださいよ

188
00:12:50.478 --> 00:12:51.353 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（二木）ええ？

189
00:12:51.479 --> 00:12:52.438 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（栗田）あ…

190
00:12:52.563 --> 00:12:55.274 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
士郎さんの花嫁候補の
お手並み拝見だわ

191
00:13:03.407 --> 00:13:07.203 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
まあ 勝手に 山岡さんの
お嫁さん候補だなんて

192
00:13:07.328 --> 00:13:08.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
失礼しちゃうわ

193
00:13:09.914 --> 00:13:14.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（二木）あの おチヨさんって人
山岡さんに影響力が強そうね

194
00:13:15.920 --> 00:13:17.505 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
よーし やるか

195
00:13:19.006 --> 00:13:19.965 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
え？ 二木さん

196
00:13:22.384 --> 00:13:23.469 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
むっ

197
00:13:39.235 --> 00:13:40.152 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（男性）もっと水だ

198
00:13:40.277 --> 00:13:41.904 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（男性）わかった
（男性）早くしろ

199
00:13:47.034 --> 00:13:48.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（栗田）えーっと

200
00:14:03.676 --> 00:14:04.677 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
うーん

201
00:14:08.514 --> 00:14:11.892 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
ああ ダイコン ニンジン
ジャガイモ コンニャク 豚肉

202
00:14:12.017 --> 00:14:13.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
そして ミカン

203
00:14:13.602 --> 00:14:14.895 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
これだけか

204
00:14:15.020 --> 00:14:17.064 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あっ こんなものがありました

205
00:14:17.648 --> 00:14:20.317 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（二木）あら 新巻ジャケね

206
00:14:23.946 --> 00:14:25.155 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
うーん…

207
00:14:25.739 --> 00:14:27.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
肉と野菜を炒めたり

208
00:14:27.533 --> 00:14:30.244 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
シャケを焼いたりしても
これだけの材料じゃ

209
00:14:30.369 --> 00:14:33.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
限られた量のものしか作れないわ

210
00:14:34.540 --> 00:14:37.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
消火作業を手伝いにくる
大勢の人たちに―

211
00:14:37.251 --> 00:14:41.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
出せるようなものを作る材料なんて
ないじゃないの

212
00:14:42.089 --> 00:14:43.841 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
おチヨさんも意地が悪いわね

213
00:14:44.884 --> 00:14:48.262 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
これだけの材料で
お手並み拝見もないもんだわ

214
00:14:48.387 --> 00:14:49.763 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
どうしよう

215
00:15:03.235 --> 00:15:04.737 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
これ 何でしょう？

216
00:15:04.862 --> 00:15:06.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（二木）
開けてみましょうよ

217
00:15:11.869 --> 00:15:12.870 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あっ

218
00:15:15.581 --> 00:15:17.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（二木）
なーんだ 酒粕(さけかす)じゃない

219
00:15:23.631 --> 00:15:24.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あっ

220
00:15:26.926 --> 00:15:28.969 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
二木さん 何とかなりそうですよ

221
00:15:29.720 --> 00:15:30.930 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
え？ それで？

222
00:15:31.889 --> 00:15:32.890 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
フフッ

223
00:15:36.644 --> 00:15:39.063 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（男性）よいしょ それっ

224
00:15:45.194 --> 00:15:46.278 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
えいっ

225
00:15:46.654 --> 00:15:47.488 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ふっ

226
00:15:47.613 --> 00:15:49.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（サイレン）

227
00:15:49.782 --> 00:15:51.283 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（男性）ああ
（男性）来た

228
00:15:58.374 --> 00:16:00.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（消防士）この奥だ
（消防士）よし わかった

229
00:16:39.415 --> 00:16:41.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（社長）
いやあ ありがとうございました

230
00:16:41.333 --> 00:16:44.003 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
皆さんには 本当に
ご迷惑をおかけしまして

231
00:16:44.503 --> 00:16:46.755 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
おかげさまで
火事はボヤで済みました

232
00:16:46.880 --> 00:16:50.050 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
この分なら 営業のほうも大して
差し支えずにやっていけそうです

233
00:16:50.175 --> 00:16:51.135 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
すいませんでした

234
00:16:51.260 --> 00:16:53.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
いやいや よかった よかった

235
00:16:54.054 --> 00:16:56.056 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ボヤで済んで何よりだよ

236
00:16:56.432 --> 00:16:58.017 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
はあ どうも

237
00:16:59.184 --> 00:17:03.105 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
それにしても ホッとしたら
何だか急に寒くなりましたな

238
00:17:03.230 --> 00:17:06.483 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
消火に夢中で 全身に水を
浴びちまいましたからな

239
00:17:06.734 --> 00:17:07.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ドアが開く音）

240
00:17:12.281 --> 00:17:14.283 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
皆さん お疲れさまでした

241
00:17:14.408 --> 00:17:16.910 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
どうぞ 温かいものでも
召し上がってください

242
00:17:17.161 --> 00:17:18.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（一同）おお

243
00:17:18.245 --> 00:17:19.872 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
何ができたのかしら？

244
00:17:23.000 --> 00:17:24.334 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（一同）わあ

245
00:17:24.877 --> 00:17:27.546 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（男性）
ああ いやあ ハッハッハ

246
00:17:27.671 --> 00:17:29.298 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
これは…

247
00:17:29.423 --> 00:17:34.261 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（男性）
いやあ おいしそうな甘酒だ
ハハハハハ…

248
00:17:34.887 --> 00:17:36.221 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（山岡）ゲッ

249
00:17:39.433 --> 00:17:41.351 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
さあ どうぞ 甘酒です

250
00:17:41.477 --> 00:17:45.064 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
甘くて熱いから 疲れもとれるし
風邪よけにもなりますよ

251
00:17:45.189 --> 00:17:46.190 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（男性）アチチ…
（二木）はい

252
00:17:46.315 --> 00:17:48.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（男性）ああ どうも
（栗田）どうぞ

253
00:17:48.901 --> 00:17:49.735 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（二木）はい どうぞ

254
00:17:49.860 --> 00:17:51.653 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（栗田）
はい 召し上がってください

255
00:17:51.779 --> 00:17:52.738 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
どうぞ

256
00:17:54.948 --> 00:17:57.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ああっ こいつはいいや

257
00:17:57.201 --> 00:17:58.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（男性）アチチッ

258
00:17:58.911 --> 00:18:03.165 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
ああっ
この不思議な甘さが何とも

259
00:18:03.499 --> 00:18:05.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
おチヨさんも試してください

260
00:18:05.292 --> 00:18:07.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（おチヨ）ああ ありがとう

261
00:18:07.836 --> 00:18:09.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
チェッ あの２人

262
00:18:09.463 --> 00:18:13.467 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
俺が大事にとっといた
大吟醸の酒粕を見つけやがったな

263
00:18:13.592 --> 00:18:14.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
おっ

264
00:18:15.636 --> 00:18:17.679 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
はい どうぞ 山岡さん

265
00:18:18.138 --> 00:18:19.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あっ どうも

266
00:18:20.390 --> 00:18:21.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
アチッ！

267
00:18:22.559 --> 00:18:24.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ああっ うまい

268
00:18:25.145 --> 00:18:27.064 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（おチヨ）
日本酒の酒粕を水で溶いて―

269
00:18:27.314 --> 00:18:31.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
沸かして 砂糖をたっぷり
隠し味に 塩をひとつまみ

270
00:18:32.402 --> 00:18:34.029 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
それだけで
こんなにすばらしい―

271
00:18:34.154 --> 00:18:36.990 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
甘酒ができるんですから
ありがたいですねえ

272
00:18:37.825 --> 00:18:38.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ねえ 士郎さん

273
00:18:38.784 --> 00:18:40.452 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（山岡）うん？ うん

274
00:18:41.537 --> 00:18:44.414 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
酒粕が上等だからだよ チッ

275
00:18:45.082 --> 00:18:47.376 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（男性）
ああ こりゃ いけるな

276
00:18:47.960 --> 00:18:49.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
本当に体が温まるよ

277
00:18:49.753 --> 00:18:51.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
酒のいい香りがたまらないね

278
00:18:51.839 --> 00:18:54.842 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
ああ　お腹にきゅーっと
しみ渡るねえ

279
00:18:54.967 --> 00:18:58.345 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
ハハハ　でも 落ち着いたら
何だか腹が減ってきたな

280
00:19:03.100 --> 00:19:05.185 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
甘酒の次はこれです

281
00:19:05.310 --> 00:19:07.271 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
たっぷり召し上がってください

282
00:19:07.688 --> 00:19:10.315 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（一同）おお…

283
00:19:10.440 --> 00:19:11.275 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
何なんだろ

284
00:19:14.444 --> 00:19:15.696 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
おお いい匂いだ

285
00:19:16.321 --> 00:19:17.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
おお これは…

286
00:19:17.781 --> 00:19:19.491 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（男性）
おお 粕汁だな

287
00:19:19.616 --> 00:19:22.244 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（男性）
シャケの粕汁だよ ハハハハ…

288
00:19:22.369 --> 00:19:23.370 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（男性）
これはおいしそうだ

289
00:19:26.790 --> 00:19:28.792 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（栗田）はい どうぞ
（男性）ああ ありがとう

290
00:19:29.418 --> 00:19:30.836 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（栗田）はい どうぞ

291
00:19:31.253 --> 00:19:32.546 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（男性）ありがとう

292
00:19:33.881 --> 00:19:36.675 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（山岡）へえ 三平汁だ

293
00:19:38.385 --> 00:19:39.928 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
本格的だな

294
00:19:41.138 --> 00:19:45.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
シャケと野菜のぶつ切りをよく煮て
それに酒粕を溶いたんだな

295
00:19:47.144 --> 00:19:50.606 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（おチヨ）野菜はジャガイモ
ニンジン ダイコン

296
00:19:50.981 --> 00:19:54.568 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
コンニャクは ちゃんと
指でちぎってありますわ

297
00:19:59.114 --> 00:20:01.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
いかがです？ お口に合いますか？

298
00:20:02.743 --> 00:20:04.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
これ ２人で作ったんですか？

299
00:20:05.370 --> 00:20:07.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
はい 甘酒は私

300
00:20:07.706 --> 00:20:09.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
三平汁は二木さんが作りました

301
00:20:09.666 --> 00:20:11.168 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
いえ 私(わたくし)は…

302
00:20:11.710 --> 00:20:14.379 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ふうん なるほどねえ

303
00:20:15.088 --> 00:20:16.715 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
お見事ですよ

304
00:20:16.840 --> 00:20:20.677 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
あれだけの材料で
これだけのものを作るなんてねえ

305
00:20:20.802 --> 00:20:25.599 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
汁物だったら こうして大勢の人に
手軽に食べてもらえますものねえ

306
00:20:26.600 --> 00:20:31.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
最初に甘酒 次に三平汁という
順序もニクいわねえ

307
00:20:32.064 --> 00:20:35.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
消火作業で疲れて
冷えた体を熱くして―

308
00:20:35.317 --> 00:20:37.611 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
甘い甘酒でホッとさせて

309
00:20:37.736 --> 00:20:40.322 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
塩味のきいた
こってりした三平汁で―

310
00:20:40.447 --> 00:20:42.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
体の芯まで満足させようなんてね

311
00:20:45.786 --> 00:20:48.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
ダシも ちゃんと昆布で
とってあるじゃないの

312
00:20:48.413 --> 00:20:49.957 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
うん 感心 感心

313
00:20:50.707 --> 00:20:51.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
お嬢さん方は

314
00:20:52.000 --> 00:20:55.170 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
私が想像していた以上に
すばらしい人たちだわねえ

315
00:20:56.004 --> 00:20:57.130 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（２人）ウフッ

316
00:20:57.965 --> 00:20:59.216 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
士郎さん

317
00:20:59.341 --> 00:21:03.095 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
こりゃ お２人のうち
どちらを選ぶか難しくなりましたね

318
00:21:03.262 --> 00:21:04.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
アハハハ…

319
00:21:05.264 --> 00:21:07.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
おチヨさん やめてくれよ

320
00:21:07.557 --> 00:21:10.102 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
本当に この２人は会社の同僚なの

321
00:21:10.227 --> 00:21:14.606 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
おやおや お嫁さんのことは
おチヨにどーんと任せてください

322
00:21:14.773 --> 00:21:17.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
いや いらないってば
お嫁さん まだいいんだってば

323
00:21:17.567 --> 00:21:23.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（一同の笑い声）

324
00:21:42.134 --> 00:21:44.553 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
今日も休めばよかったのに

325
00:21:45.846 --> 00:21:47.514 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
まだ 風邪 治ってないんじゃ
ないんですか？

326
00:21:48.265 --> 00:21:49.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
冗談じゃねえや

327
00:21:49.891 --> 00:21:52.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
うちにいると おチヨさんに
何言われっか わかんないからな

328
00:21:53.145 --> 00:21:54.229 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ヘックション

329
00:21:54.354 --> 00:21:58.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
それなら 会社に出て副部長に
どなられたほうが まだ休まるよ

330
00:21:58.525 --> 00:21:59.443 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ヘ… ヘックション！

331
00:22:10.370 --> 00:22:12.039 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（戸が開く音）

332
00:22:12.164 --> 00:22:14.082 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（岡星(おかぼし)精一）おや いらっしゃい
（冬美(ふゆみ)）あら いらっしゃいませ

333
00:22:15.083 --> 00:22:15.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
よう

334
00:22:17.169 --> 00:22:18.462 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
どうも

335
00:22:18.587 --> 00:22:20.047 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
こんばんは

336
00:22:24.009 --> 00:22:27.345 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
栗田さん きのうの三平汁
うまくいきましたか？

337
00:22:28.638 --> 00:22:30.057 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あっ え… ええ

338
00:22:30.265 --> 00:22:31.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
まあ…

339
00:22:31.933 --> 00:22:33.769 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
三平汁？

340
00:22:34.394 --> 00:22:36.730 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
電話じゃ 十分お教えできなくて

341
00:22:37.272 --> 00:22:39.649 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
ああっ どうも
よくできたと思ったら

342
00:22:39.775 --> 00:22:41.777 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
岡星さんに電話で教わったのか

343
00:22:42.736 --> 00:22:43.570 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
エッヘヘ

344
00:22:43.695 --> 00:22:47.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
でも 三平汁と甘酒を
発想したのは栗田さんよ

345
00:22:47.574 --> 00:22:49.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
私なんか お手伝いしただけ

346
00:22:49.993 --> 00:22:51.661 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
クソーッ バラしてやる

347
00:22:51.787 --> 00:22:53.622 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
おチヨさんに
真相バラしてやるからな

348
00:22:54.289 --> 00:22:56.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
じゃあ 呼びましょうか？
おチヨさん ここに

349
00:22:57.125 --> 00:22:59.544 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
え？ え？ ええ…

350
00:22:59.669 --> 00:23:02.923 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ワハハハハハ…

351
00:23:04.216 --> 00:23:06.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
やめてくれ
それだけはやめてくれ

352
00:23:06.468 --> 00:23:08.136 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
また 嫁さんの話になる

353
00:23:08.261 --> 00:23:13.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（一同の笑い声）

354
00:23:16.937 --> 00:23:22.943 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
♪～

